          "text": "This session uses interval training to develop aerobic power \u2014 the ability to sustain high output in the oxidative energy system. The 90-second ski erg intervals with 1:1 work:rest ratio train the upper threshold of aerobic capacity. The EMOM metcon maintains cardiovascular demand across three monostructural modalities, developing the ability to recover quickly between efforts.",
